## wedit

([wedit.io](https://wedit.io)) - ([GitHub](https://github.com/sofmon/wedit))

Wedit uses static HTML website as template and allows content to be changed through WYSIWYG editing using the web browser.

All changes are immediate and align with the intended website design.

## arke.app (work in progress)

(arke.app) - (GitHub)

Decentralized, server-less, point to point encrypted messenger app: No servers; No sniffing; No control; No influence.
